## Troubleshooting

| Problem | Cause | Fix |
|---------|-------|-----|
| DHT11 reads NaN | Missing 10kΩ pull-up resistor | Add 10kΩ between DATA and VCC |
| DHT11 always 0.0°C | Wrong pin number | Check `#define PIN_DHT` matches wiring |
| Gas always 0 | MQ sensor on 3.3V | Connect MQ VCC to 5V |
| Gas always 4095 | Sensor needs warmup | Wait 24-48h for new MQ sensor |
| Railway fetch failed | HTTPS SSL issue | Use v6.1 with `setInsecure()` |
| Firebase push fails | Wrong rules | Set `.read`/`.write` = true |
| Fan not turning | Active-LOW confusion | LOW signal = relay ON |
| Buzzer no sound | Active vs passive | Use passive buzzer with `tone()` |
| WiFi timeout | Wrong credentials or 5GHz | ESP32 supports 2.4GHz only |

